                    <p class="mbr-text mbr-fonts-style display-7" id="team_diagnosis_description">
                         Many companies each year look for ways to understand employee engagement. Some of the most known surveys are run by Gallup, Great Place to Work and Perceptyx. Those surveys give a great picture of how employees fill about they company they work for from a departmnet and management level.
						 However, those surveys are not designed to measure perspectives of the small, cross-functional, self-organizing deelopment teams. Also, they only measure engeagement once a year. In software development, things are contiunously changing.
						 A faster feedback loop is needed to be successful.
						 </p>	 
