                <div class="text-wrapper">
                    <h3 class="mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3 display-5"><strong>Prescribing Team Health Checks</strong></h3>
                    <p class="mbr-text mbr-fonts-style display-7" id="team_diagnosis_description">
                         A team health check is self-assesment done by a team using different health indicators to see what's working and what's not. The questions are designed to help expand each team memebrs perspective. It provides a balanced perspective showing the good things
						 as well as the pain points.
						 </p>	
					<p class="mbr-text mbr-fonts-style display-7" id="team_diagnosis_description">
                         Teamhealth checks successfully impact the team if they are taken at least once a quarter.
						 </p>	 	 
