                <div class="text-wrapper">
                    <h3 class="mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3 display-5"><strong>How Does This App Help With A Team Health Check </strong></h3>
                    <p class="mbr-text mbr-fonts-style display-7" id="team_diagnosis_description">
                        This application  displays a real time look into the good things and pain points of a team. Once a team ans its members have been added to the app they will be able to see two views.
						<br>
						The first view displays the overall team diagnosis, which is the average score of all of the health indicators of the team. The second view, displays the indivudal indicators of the team member. On the indiviudal team member page, the team member can make updates at anytime
